lines.text: I'm gonna call the Ghostbusters on your ass!
You should forget females. Stick to Nintendo.
Or better yet let's go down to the cemetery and get laid. I need some action.

[At urinal]
Look, we've been through a lot together and I love you more than anything in this world, but you've got to stop popping up all the time wanting to play. I'm on a date, I can't play with you right now. Gosh, you're making it so hard. People are starting to stare at me.
You know something, I've got the same problem.
Trust me, my problem's a lot bigger than yours.
Halloween's gonna be the bomb this year.
Kenny, there's no way he can dunk it. He's just too small.
Shut up, Zigi! You're seven feet tall and you can't touch the rim!
At least I'm seven feet tall!
